me.taylorkelly.mywarp.bukkit

Class BukkitAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.bukkit.BukkitAdapter

  • public final class BukkitAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
    Adapts between equivalent local and Bukkit objects.

    Operations of this class are always stateless. Conversions that depend on a state are available in MyWarpPlugin.
